metadata.name: Seedling
metadata.description:
Oh seedling, in earth's rich soil you lay,  
So small and simple, yet so full of potential each day.  
With roots that reach deep, and stem that grows tall,  
Your journey is just beginning, before you conquer all.

You hold within you, the promise of life,  
With petals that bloom, and leaves that will thrive.  
A symbol of hope, a reminder so bright,  
That beauty and growth, are always within sight.

So let your spirit soar, let your roots grow strong,  
With each passing moment, you'll be where you belong.  
In the garden of life, you'll spread your wings,  
And show the world, the potential that becoming brings.

This artwork was gifted to individuals who participated in the 1st Jeremy Grows feedback survey as a token of gratitude and thanks. Their support is the sun and the rain that have allowed this seedling to sprout. Thank you for contributing to the future success of our community.
